SummaryEnglish: The story centers on Yuhi and Yuamu, two twins who spend their time searching for aliens using a mysterious device made by Yuhi. While their research never really leads to much, they eventually discover an actual spaceship, in which they meet Yudias, an alien traveler believed to have come from a distant region of space! The latter came to Earth to participate in the famous Rush Duels, in order to offer a new future to his comrades who had to leave their home planet due to war...

1.SummaryEnglish: Various artists and voice actors come together to perform iconic songs from Go Rush live!

1.TitleEnglish: We're the Ultraterrestrial Trouble Solutions Consultancy!
1.SummaryEnglish: The twins Yuamu and Yuhi are grade-schoolers who live in Mutsuba Town, and they manage a consultancy known as Ultraterrestrial Trouble Solutions, or UTS for short. When they were looking for an alien that’s been kidnapping cats, they encountered an alien warrior named Yudias on a stranded spaceship.

2.TitleEnglish: The Organization for Monitoring Interstellar Kriminals
2.SummaryEnglish: UTS has a new client, who turns out to be Sogetsu Manabu, an agent of the MIK organization! He demands that Yudias turns himself in for being a troublesome illegal alien. And so, Yudias Duels against Manabu, with his freedom on the line!

3.SummaryEnglish: There has been a series of attacks in Mutsuba Town. One victim was looking at cards. Another just finished a drawing. And then there’s Yagi from UTS. At first glance, there seems to be no connection between the victims, but as it turns out, they all have something in common…

4.SummaryEnglish: Chupataro lured Yudias to a garbage disposal area. Thanks to his inborn abilities, Yudias was able to overcome Chupataro’s many traps, but he still ended up getting captured! Meanwhile, Yuhi, who was panicking, also arrived at the garbage disposal area…

5.TitleEnglish: I'm Kawai Tell, and I'm Parched
5.SummaryEnglish: Yuhi is angry that the clothes he sent to a dry cleaning shop are soaking wet, so he confronts the shop’s manager about it. But as it turns out, the manager is actually Kawai Tell, the alien who stole Yuhi’s Earthdamar! Yuhi challenges Kawai to a Duel, but since his Duel Disk is soaking wet, he can’t activate it…

6.TitleEnglish: Whether You Believe It or Not Is Not My Problem
6.SummaryEnglish: Yuhi and his friends investigate an urban legend.

7.TitleEnglish: Can You Name All the Monster Types?
7.SummaryEnglish: Feeling that he’s still not good enough, Yudias asked Yuhi for a special Rush Duel training session. Yuhi used the Special Training Mecha and the Special Training CD to train Yudias. Yudias was able to answer every question, and his training seemed to be going well, but then the Special Training Mecha went out of control…

8.TitleEnglish: Good Manya-nya from the TV Kingdom
8.SummaryEnglish: Atachi Manya, a talented child actress, will be starring in the only show that is popular on Mutsuba Cable TV: “Learning the Fun Way – Ultimate Go Rush!” Yuamu, her childhood friend, was asked to Duel her. The two haven’t seen each other for five years, and Yuamu couldn’t help but be bewildered after seeing how Manya has changed…

9.SummaryEnglish: Manya’s team is having a Rush Duel battle against a local elementary school team. The opponent Manya picked for the second match is Sogetsu Manabu, who was part of the audience. And the duelist Manabu will be facing is: Manya’s pet dog, Bochi?!

10.SummaryEnglish: Chupataro barged into Mutsuba Cable TV’s studio and caused a ruckus, demanding a Duel. A concerned Yudias volunteered to take him on. However, the moment Chupataro summoned Magical Sheep Girl Meeeg-chan, his Duel Disk started emitting a strange light…

11.SummaryEnglish: Manabu asks Yudias if he knows where Zwijo is. It seems that Zwijo is linked to the incident that happened at Mutsuba Cable TV’s studio the other day. Realizing how powerless he is, Yudias decides to train some more. And so, Manya suggests a special training session from hell to him!

12.SummaryEnglish: Trusting his hunch, Yudias heads to Mutsuba Tower along with his friends, and finally manages to find Zuwijo. Zuwijo is planning to use Rush Duels and the Earthdamar as tools for war. In order to stop his commander, who has gone down the wrong path, Yudias challenges him to a Rush Duel!

13.SummaryEnglish: Two alien warriors are trying to bring peace to the Velgear Cluster. One is learning about Rush Duels in order to end all conflicts, while the other is trying to weaponize Rush Duels in order to achieve victory over his foes. As their unwavering ideals clash, the battle between Yudias and Zuwijo finally reach a conclusion!

14.SummaryEnglish: Kirishima London approaches UTS and requests them to look for a missing girl in the Alien Residential Area, located underground. However, Mr. Tazaki doesn’t want Yuhi and his friends to go to such a dangerous area, so he challenges their client, London, to a Duel!

15.SummaryEnglish: In order to look for Goha Yuna, Yuhi and co. head to the Alien Residential Area. However, just as they begin their search, three siblings who call themselves the Jersey Devils block their path. With the mysterious power known as “Duel Power” at stake, Yudias and the eldest brother George Jersey begin their Duel!

16.SummaryEnglish: Yuhi and co. heard from George that there’s an informant who knows where Yuna is. Unable to find the informant, they returned to UTS. As Yuhi was taking a bath to relax, the light suddenly turned off. He then heard a creepy chorus…

17.SummaryEnglish: The informant, Fisher Sky, has appeared. Ever since that incident with Zuwijo, Sky has been very interested in Yudias. Yuamu wants more information on Yuna, so she challenges Sky to a Duel, with information about Yudias as a bargaining chip. A high-level Information Warfare Duel ensues!

18.SummaryEnglish: Yuhi and co. learned that Yuna might be at Badloon Castle. However, the only people who can enter the castle are Duelists who possess the “macho” rank, which is the highest rank in Dueling. So, in order to become macho Duelists, Yuhi and co. visit a colosseum where ruffians gather, known as the Coruffium. Yuhi’s first battle is against a mysterious prophet known as Nomratdamas.

19.SummaryEnglish: Yuhi and co. were going to keep Dueling in the Coruffium, but Manabu told them to not come to the Alien Residential Area. Nanahoshi Ranran, the chief of MIK, then showed up out of nowhere and declared that the lawless Alien Residential Area must be sealed off immediately! What action will Manabu take in response to Ranran?

20.SummaryEnglish: As Yudias and co. try to look for clues about Goha Yuna in the Coruffium, a girl wearing a cloak appears before them. The girl asks them if they have some business with her leader, Rovian. In order to gain more information about Rovian, the master of Badloon Castle, Yudias challenges the girl to a Duel.

21.SummaryEnglish: Yuhi and co. return to the surface to do some sleuthing about Goha Yuna. However, even though they’re about to start their investigation, Yudias is nowhere to be found. As they investigate the Goha Company, a fragment of Fisher Sky, Navel No. 81, informs them that Yudias is in danger.

22.SummaryEnglish: Yuhi and Yuamu enter Badloon Castle to rescue Yudias, who has been captured. In order to do that, they face off against Kirishima Rovian, the leader of the Rovian Bandits, in a 2v1 Duel. The Ohdo twins put up a good fight, but now, they must fight the Queen of Badloon Castle at her full strength.

23.SummaryEnglish: In a town under the underground area, known as “Under-Underground Town,” Yuhi and co. find a tsukemen restaurant in an alley. They see that they can get one free drink, so they go inside the restaurant and enjoy some exquisite tsukemen made by Oomori Menjaburo. However, Menjaburo’s true identity is actually…

24.SummaryEnglish: Yuhi and co. managed to rescue Yudias. But there’s a problem: he’s been turned into a shirt! Yuhi and co. try various ways to return him back to normal, but end up losing sight of him. As they go look for Yudias once again, they find a card in the park.

25.SummaryEnglish: Goha Yuna and Rovian unexpectedly show up at UTS’s office. Yuna demands Yuhi and co. to hand their office over. This angers Yuhi greatly, but despite that, Yudias still challenges Rovian to a Duel, with UTS itself at stake. After receiving some encouragement from Yuamu, Yudias begins the Duel, aiming for a new Velgeard at the same time!

26.SummaryEnglish: Rovian drives Yudias into a corner with her Equip Spells. However, Yudias is still determined to beat Rovian, even though the odds are stacked against him. As Yudias starts enjoying the Duel, a miracle occurs in Mutsuba Town!

27.SummaryEnglish: Magical Sheep Girl Meeeg-chan’s popularity has tanked because of Chupataro. In order to restore her image, Chupataro decides to make an anime about her. He starts producing the anime with the full cooperation of UTS. However, they immediately run into some very serious production issues…

28.SummaryEnglish: Mutsuba Asaka is the president of Mutsuba Heavy Machinery, which controls Mutsuba Town. In order to free the Valvelgear, which is being exploited as a power source by Asaka, Yuhi challenges Asaka to a Duel. Yuhi might not have a Duel Disk, but he has reliable allies who will back him up!

29.SummaryEnglish: At Asaka’s request, Yuhi and Yuamu go to the riverside to look for a complainer. There, they find the complainer, Glatt Ishida, doing rock balancing with Yudias. When the rock pile is knocked over because of vibration, Ishida decides to go complain to Asaka. So, Yudias tries to stop Ishida with a Duel…

30.SummaryEnglish: UTS’s dinner table is loaded with a mountain of curry breads! It seems that Yuamu, who’s always on the hunt for promotion campaigns, is targeting some plates that can be obtained by collecting the stickers that come with the curry breads. However, when Yuamu brings the stickers to the bakery, she learns that the plates are out of stock. So, she decides to go complain to the manager, but as it turns out…

31.SummaryEnglish: According to Rovian’s space poems and the prophecy of Camos the hat alien, the Great King of Terror will be attacking soon. Mutsuba Heavy Machinery is holding a meeting to decide on a countermeasure against this threat, but is then contacted by Ranran out of nowhere. In order to decide who will be in charge of combating the Great King of Terror, Ranran and Asaka begin a remote Rush Duel!

32.TitleEnglish: Invasion! The Great King of Terror
32.SummaryEnglish: As snow dances in the sky, a giant shadow looms over Mutsuba Town… As it turns out, it’s actually the spaceship of the Great King of Terror! Yuhi and co. bravely board the spaceship to confront him, but he then suggests a “Friendship Rush Duel Tournament.” The first match is between the Great King and Rovian! Just how powerful is the Great King of Terror?!

33.SummaryEnglish: It is now the second match of the Friendship Rush Duel Tournament, hosted by the Great King of Terror from the Arctic Nebula. Manya will be fighting against the space dinosaur, The☆Mokeida Mbembe! Mbembe rambles on about his love for plastic models. However, Manya doesn’t care about plastic models at all. She’ll be fighting against Mbembe with a Cleaning Deck!

34.SummaryEnglish: The new cards designed by Mutsuba Heavy Machinery to counter the Great King of Terror were never delivered. Nyandestar headed to Mutsuba Heavy Machinery’s office, but the group couldn’t get in touch with her, so they started getting worried. Before they knew it, it was time for the next match of the tournament. Manabu will be Dueling on behalf of Mutsuba Town. Shockingly enough, the one who will Duel Manabu is actually…!

35.SummaryEnglish: Yuhi and co. managed to capture London, but he then escaped. He left behind a cassette tape for them on the desk. The tape conveys London’s grim resolve. The message on it reads: “By the time you listen to this tape, I’ll definitely be challenging that Great King dude to a Rush Duel for sure. It’s showtime!”

36.TitleEnglish: Feelings I Want to Convey, Yei!
36.SummaryEnglish: London and others have risked their lives to uncover the truth behind the Great King. It’s about his terrifying power, which not even he is aware of. As part of the plan to seal away the Great King’s power, Yuamu takes part in the Friendship Rush Duel Tournament. However, her opponent, The☆Yeti Yukio, seems to also have another plan in mind…

37.SummaryEnglish: Zuwijo is posing as the Great King's subordinate in order to infiltrate his ship and obtain his power. He boasts that he will use any means in order to obtain more power. Unable to tolerate Zuwijo's ruthlessness, Yuhi challenges him to a Friendship Rush Duel!

38.SummaryEnglish: The☆Lugh releases a massive amount of negative energy, which can potentially engulf the whole universe. Goha Yuna and Yudias team up in order to bring The☆Lugh to justice for all the terror he's caused! Thus begins a Tag Rush Duel with the peace of the whole universe on the line!

39.SummaryEnglish: Something abnormal happens to Yuna during the Duel with The☆Lugh, but she is saved by a boy. He's the same boy who once entrusted Yudias with a Duel Disk and some cards. In order to turn the Duel around, the boy from the future takes over for Yuna and fights alongside Yudias against The ☆ Lugh !

40.SummaryEnglish: The group decides to take a detour and head to the Pawtner Planet to save Nyandestar’s family. Yuhi wants to do some Rush Duel training along the way, so he creates a makeshift training hall. As everyone gathers at the training hall, it never dawns on them that the training is all about summoning chants!

41.TitleEnglish: The Miracle of the Pawtner Planet
41.SummaryEnglish: The group succeeded in thawing the people of the Pawtner Planet. Their celebration was short-lived, however, as Dinova Velgear, a woman who called herself Zuwijo’s right-hand woman, appeared before them. Mitsuko wants to know where Zuwijo is, so she challenges Dinova to a Duel!

42.SummaryEnglish: In order to get to the Velgear Cluster, Yudias and co. head to the Mine Planet to look for Goradonium, a metal that is required for way-faster-than-light travel. There, they run into a boy named Shewbahha, who is also looking for Goradonium. Thus begins a Duel between Yuhi and Shewbahha over the rare metal.

43.TitleEnglish: Are You Fine with Me Whispering to You?
43.SummaryEnglish: Ranran just can’t handle the Earthdamar, a substance that is very much the opposite of “cute.” Guided by some mysterious whispers, Ranran attempts to conquer her fear toward the Earthdamar. However, as it turns out, the source of the whispers is Zuwijo’s subordinate, Muda Velgear, who is after the Earthdamar!

44.SummaryEnglish: Valvelgear mistakenly travels to the Dudi Ducasse star system, a frontier of the Velgear Cluster. The warriors of the Dudi Fleet then invade Mutsuba Town! Yudias teams up with the citizens of Mutsuba Town in order to break through their encirclement, so that he can go talk to the fleet’s commander…

45.SummaryEnglish: In order to show the Dudi Fleet’s commander, Dudi Nishaw, that Rush Duels can end the war in the Velgear Cluster, Yudias challenges him to a Duel! However, as Nishaw starts fretting over what he should do, a strange space is generated in the vicinity…

46.SummaryEnglish: A mysterious object has crashed into Mutsuba Town. As it turns out, it’s actually an energy being that has flown all the way from Earth. According to Manabu, the being could potentially possess anyone who was near the crash site. As Manabu goes look for the person who is possessed, he challenges Rovian to a Duel, since she’s been acting rather strangely.

47.SummaryEnglish: Something strange is going on with the Ohdo twins. Yuamu has been unusually cheerful and laughing like a maniac. Meanwhile, Yuhi starts talking about demolishing the UTS building and constructing a high-rise apartment complex in its place. And so, a strange Duel begins between the twins, with the position of president on the line!

48.TitleEnglish: The Velgear Planet in Imminent Danger
48.SummaryEnglish: Yuamu and Yuhi manage to reach the Velgear Planet thanks to the power of Damamu. The overexcited Damamu drags them around the planet, and they end up in a Duel training facility for Velgearian soldiers. Yuhi and Yuamu are then forced to undergo training along with the new recruits. However, the moment they take their eyes off Damamu, something strange occurs…

49.SummaryEnglish: Zuwijo has captured the Velgearian Supreme Council and declared that he will use Rush Duels in the war! Yudias, who has come to Yuhi’s rescue, objects to Zuwjio’s declaration. In order to figure out what the correct path is, Yudias challenges Zuwijo to a Duel!

50.SummaryEnglish: The final showdown between Yudias and Zuwijo begins, with the future of the Velgear Cluster on the line. Their fateful battle takes place in space, with their battleships facing each other. And thus, an unprecedented Battleship Rush Duel unfolds!

51.SummaryEnglish: Yudias and Zuwijo are fighting with everything they’ve got in order to achieve their ideals. However, as their intense battle rages on, the cruel fate the Velgearians have to shoulder only becomes more apparent. Yudias Velgear, the warrior who runs through the battlefield called Rush Duels, will now shoulder everything and create a path to a better future for the galaxy!

52.SummaryEnglish: Having finished the battle in the Velgear Cluster, Yudias decides to return to Earth in order to inform Yuhi and the others. The members of UTS welcome Yudias back. Time has passed, but they’re still more or less the same, and Yudias is happy to be able to see them again. However, at the same time, he feels that there is something off…

53.TitleEnglish: The Life of Yuhi the Runaway
53.SummaryEnglish: Yuhi has run away from home. Having distanced himself from UTS and Rush Duels, he’s now hanging out with his delinquent friends and engaging in all kinds of mischief. As he wanders around while being tormented by his own powerlessness, he witnesses the commander of MIK, Ryugu Phaser, having a Duel with “that guy.”

54.SummaryEnglish: Due to Operation MIK, aliens and people who associate with them have been driven to the underground Alien Residential Area. In an act of defiance, Yuna heads back to the Goha Company by herself. There, she finds Manabu waiting for her in the president’s office. In order to find out where Phaser is, she challenges Manabu to a Duel!

55.SummaryEnglish: It’s a usual morning for Yuamu. She does her work at UTS, and then rushes to school. Her school is currently holding a student council election. Through an unexpected turn of events, Yuamu and Asaka will now have a Duel to decide which one of them will be the student council president.

56.SummaryEnglish: Yuamu and her friends have formed a resistance movement against MIK. Meanwhile, Yuhi is still feeling conflicted about Rush Duels. Through pure coincidence, he encounters Ranran, who is on the run from MIK. He then has a confrontation with Tremolo, the one who is going after Ranran. What will Yuhi’s decision be?

57.TitleEnglish: The Operation to Take Back the Surface
57.SummaryEnglish: Asaka and her rebel army lead an assault on Mutsuba Heavy Industry’s card printing plant, taking down multiple MIK members through Dueling. However, an MIK commander named Energy Kopiko stands in their way! Meanwhile, Yuamu’s group sneaks into the Goha Company, and discovers something in the basement.

58.SummaryEnglish: Having obtained MIK’s most vital secret, Manabu pays a visit to UTS, but is marked as a traitor and captured. When Zuwijo shows up out of nowhere, UTS welcomes him back with open arms. Manabu doesn’t agree with this, so he challenges Zuwijo to a Duel in order to prove himself!

59.SummaryEnglish: Yudias spots Tremolo entering the Coruffium. He challenges Tremolo to a Duel in order to avenge Yuhi. Tremolo has broken the rules and entered the Coruffium in order to track down Fisher Sky, the alien who has been spying on him and his brother. There is a secret that he wants to protect, no matter what.

60.SummaryEnglish: Yuhi and That One Guy Who Invented Rush Duels have risked their lives to find out the truth behind the phenomenon that turns Duelists into cards. As Yuamu follows in That Guy’s footsteps and tries to figure this out, she runs into Phaser. Through her intense Duel with Phaser, she will reach the truth.

61.SummaryEnglish: Yuamu notices that she’s now in a strange place that resembles a Field Spell. She then hears some familiar voices. As it turns out, they’re the voices of the friends she’s lost! However, despite being able to reunite with them, Yuamu seems rather disconcerted...

62.SummaryEnglish: Yuhi, Yuamu, and That Guy have been thrown out of the strange dimension they were trapped in. They find themselves in a near-future city that is somewhat similar to Mutsuba Town. It seems that this is the world That Guy lived in. As That Guy talks about the reason why he created Rush Duels, he runs into a certain person along the way.

63.SummaryEnglish: Phaser uses Yuhi and the other carded people as hostages in order to pressure Yudias into helping out with Operation MIK. Yudias agonizes over what choice he should make, but upon learning that there is a way to return the carded people back to normal, he decides to face Phaser in a Duel, with the fate of all his friends on the line!

64.TitleEnglish: Those Who Are Born on the Star
64.SummaryEnglish: Phaser's secret is finally revealed. A kind brother who has sworn to protect his little brother from aliens, he himself is also burdened with a tragic fate. Yudias remains resolute in the face of Phaser’s overwhelming power. His strong belief in his friends and everything he cherishes will help him reach a new height.

65.SummaryEnglish: Shewbahha is delivering a package to Earth, but he has no idea where the destination is. Yudias decides to help him out. The two manage to find Kallister Gears, the place that is written on the delivery form. There, they encounter people wearing strange clothes...

66.SummaryEnglish: The Galaxy Cup, a Rush Duel tournament for both Earthlings and aliens, has finally begun! Yudias is now the Duel Tutor for the head of Kallister Gears, Ehoko Kamijo, aka Epoch. In order to allow Epoch to experience what a Duel is like, Yudias challenges Yuamu to a Duel!

67.SummaryEnglish: A mysterious masked Duelist who calls himself “Commander Study” has showed up at the Galaxy Cup! He has been farming points by picking off weak opponents. However, one man stands against him to stop his misdeeds. That man’s name is Sogetsu Maguto!

68.SummaryEnglish: Yudias has been teaching Epoch Dueling strategies, as well as how to build a Deck. Now, it's time for her to apply what she's learned! As they look for an opponent for Epoch to Duel in the Galaxy Cup, the Rush Battler sends its light toward Yuhi.

69.SummaryEnglish: Yuamu's team has been trying to uncover how the carding system works. Dinois suspects that Phaser is hiding some secret about the Relic, so she confronts Tremolo about it. The fact that someone is suspecting his brother doesn't sit well with him. On top of that, he's also having suspicions about Zuwijo, Dinois's commander. And so, he challenges Dinois to a Duel.

70.SummaryEnglish: Zaion, a representative of Providence, the galactic company that sells furniture for cheap, has attacked Mutsuba Town! Zaion approaches Epoch about making high-power gears at an exorbitant price, scaring her with threats in the process. In order to protect Epoch, Yudias challenges Zaion to a Duel!

71.SummaryEnglish: The Providence Galactic Furniture Store has been around for generations. However, it's been repeatedly struck by galactic recessions and raids from other furniture stores. After Zaion became its manager, it's been constantly struggling with financial problems. Zaion's dream is to have 88.8 billion Providence stores across the whole universe. What will become of his dream as his Duel with Yudias comes to an end?

72.SummaryEnglish: It's time for the Galaxy Cup's much-anticipated finals! The first battle is between Mitsuko and Zuwijo. Mitsuko is burning with rage because Zuwijo has been giving her the cold shoulder. However, she’s having a hard time against Zuwijo's fierce attack. As she tries to counterattack, she draws a card she's never seen before...!

73.SummaryEnglish: The finals continue with three exciting match-ups: Asaka vs Kawai, Rovian vs Yuna, and Yuamu vs Nyandestar. As they clash against each other with their ideals and pride on the line, a strange phenomenon occurs! Cards that shouldn't exist will turn the Duelists' destinies upside down...

74.SummaryEnglish: Yuna challenges Rovian to a Duel during the finals. She has always loved Rovian since she was a child, but as That Guy becomes more and more important to her, her feelings also become muddled up. What is the road she has found by facing Rovian with everything she's got?

75.SummaryEnglish: Yudias encounters Phaser in the labyrinth during the finals. Phaser seems to have some kind of motive for standing in Yudias's way. Meanwhile, as Yuhi and the others head to the Relic, where they bear witness to a terrifying project.

76.SummaryEnglish: Created on a planet at the edge of the universe, he gradually obtained more comrades and gave rise to a massive civilization in the Velgear Star Cluster. One day, he was drawn to Rush Duels, setting everything in motion in the process. The shocking truth will now be revealed as Kuaidul Velgear, the first of the Kartumata, makes his entrance!

77.SummaryEnglish: It's time for the final battle of the Galaxy Cup. Yudias faces off against Yuhi, but ends up clashing against Kuaidul and getting trapped in his mental world. Just what are the memories sealed deep within Kuaidul's mind? Yuhi will now put an end to Velgear's sorrowful creation story!

78.SummaryEnglish: It's early in the afternoon, and Yudias is taking a leisurely walk with his friends in the park. But then, Chupataro suddenly shows up and demands Meeeg-chan to be returned to him! Meanwhile, Damamu is reveling in Fusion. Mutsuba Town has gone back to normal after the end of the Galaxy Cup, but Yuhi can't help but feel that there is something off...

79.SummaryEnglish: Everything is getting stranger by the second as Mutsuba Town is enveloped by the Kuaidul Spacetime. It seems that as long as no one realizes that something is off, they won't be able to return to their true selves. Yuhi and others sense that there is something abnormal going on, so they inform everyone about it, but Manabu refuses to believe them. And so, Yuamu Duels against Manabu to convince him!

80.SummaryEnglish: At long last, Zaion has achieved his dream and opened 88.8 billion Providence stores in the whole universe! But as it turns out, this is all an illusion created by the Kuaidul Spacetime! Yuhi pays Zaion a visit in order to tell him the truth, but he just wouldn't listen. And so, Yuhi challenges Zaion to a Duel in order to wake him up from this false dream!

81.SummaryEnglish: At Mutsuba Tower, Yuhi and co. run into Asaka and Tell, who are both acting strange. They try to persuade the two but are instead arrested and subjected to harsh treatment. In order to make Asaka see reason, Yudias challenges her to a Duel, but she seems to have other ideas...

82.SummaryEnglish: The people at the Boiled Bagel Requiem bakery have also fallen victim to the Kuaidul Dimension. Dinois claims that she is the star of Boiled Bagel Requiem, the best bakery in town! As she gets more and more out of control, Zuwijo tries to stop her through a Rush Duel.

83.SummaryEnglish: Yudias and co. find a suspicious house. There, they encounter Yuna, who is cuddling a baby. They also get caught up in her delusion and are transformed, becoming more adorable than before... In order to escape this delusion, Yuhi challenges Yuna to a Duel! "Wush Duew, goo goo gaga!"

84.SummaryEnglish: "Nice shot!" A basketball hoop shouts out of nowhere. As it turns out, it's a friend of Mitsuko from the Three-Meter Planet, Tamako Kago, who is also known as Big Sis Goalko Baske. Both her and Mitsuko are acting strange, so in order to snap them out of it, Yuamu and Epoch challenge them to a two-on-two Duel!

85.SummaryEnglish: Yuhi and others wake up in an unfamiliar classroom. Gathered in there are the 39 people who have realized the truth about the Kuaidul Space-Time. Meanwhile, Yudias and Kuaidul are outside the classroom. The two of them begin a Duel, with the freedom of the 39 people trapped in the classroom at stake!

86.SummaryEnglish: Ange, Liem and Karen are now following Phaser around and calling themselves the Phaser Girls. They've been like this ever since the Kuaidul Dimension was created. Having been robbed of his secretaries, Tremolo challenges Phaser to a Duel, with the MIK Commander position at stake. Thus, begins what is known as the Kotatsu Rebellion!

87.SummaryEnglish: It seems there's a reason why Kuaidul can't turn Yudias into a card. There's a powerful lock on Yudias's mind, which prevents him from realizing the truth about the Kuaidul Dimension. In order to remove this lock, Operation: "Make Yudias Realize!" is put into action! What will you do, Yudias?

88.SummaryEnglish: Yuhi and others have been gathered in the Other Dimension Classroom to be used as Kuaidul's pawns once again. However, they are able to escape from his control thanks to Yudias, who has realized the truth behind the Kuaidul Dimension. Yudias and his 39 allies will now face off against Kuaidul together!

89.SummaryEnglish: Yudias is fighting against Kuaidul in order to free everyone from the Kuaidul Space-Time. As their Duel rages on, vivid images of the galaxies surface in their minds. Something abnormal then happens to Kuaidul. What fate awaits the Proto-Velgear as he tries to achieve his grand dream?

90.SummaryEnglish: Two warriors are engaging in a fierce battle over the fates of two galaxies, the Milky Way and the Andromeda Galaxy. Kuaidul is planning to fuse the two galaxies together once the Duel is over. A shocking truth is also revealed as their Duel reaches its end!

91.SummaryEnglish: Kuaidul told Yudias about the cruel fate all Velgearians will suffer. Yuhi and co. are desperately looking for a way to change this grim future. Yuhi learns that the Chapeau aliens are having a secret meeting, so he disguises himself as a Chapeau alien to sneak into the meeting and ask Camos, who has prophetic powers, about the future of the Velgearians...

92.SummaryEnglish: In order to save the Velgearians, Yuga's knowledge will be required. Yuamu and co. use Manya's connections to help look for Yuga. They visit a studio to film a movie, but run into Bochi, who has previously disappeared after saying that he won't come back until he's become a star. And so, Manya begins a Duel against Bochi to punish him!

93.SummaryEnglish: Zaion has coughed up his gear and lost the ability to create furniture. Yuhi and co. want to restore his ability in order to help repair the Relic. They try to make him swallow the gear again, but he refuses, so they decide to settle this matter with a Duel. The one who will be facing Zaion is The☆Lugh, the alien he has served for many years.

94.SummaryEnglish: As she tries to figure out what she should do about the Velgearians' crisis, Rovian pays the UTS office a visit. While she is helping the UTS staff clean up, she finds the guitar of Princess Minstrel, the one who once taught her about space poems. The owner of the guitar turns out to be...

95.SummaryEnglish: The 8.88 million Velgearians are nearing the end of their lifespan, and they want Tazaki to keep it a secret from Yudias. Tazaki agrees, and asks Asaka for help with this, but she vehemently refuses. Not wanting to give up, Tazaki challenges Asaka to a Duel!

96.SummaryEnglish: Yuna is waiting at the vending machine area, where Yuga is supposed to show up. However, Yuga ends up getting captured by Manabu's device. Determined to see Yuga no matter what, Yuna challenges Manabu to a Duel once again. If she wins, Manabu will have to let her see Yuga!

97.SummaryEnglish: Dinois and Muda interrupt the analysis of the robot that was found in the Relic. Having accepted the fate of the Velgearians, the two of them steal the robot, and then challenge Yuhi and Yuamu to a Tag Duel. Despite Dinois and Muda's desperate efforts, the end of their lives is still fast approaching...

98.SummaryEnglish: As tragedy is about to strike, Zuwijo feels an uncontrollable urge, as well as joy. The moment he learns what this mysterious emotion is, he decides to challenge Yudias to a Duel. It's a Duel that no one will be able to stop. Zuwijo zir Velgear's final battle will now begin.

99.SummaryEnglish: The Alien Middle School is temporarily closed for the day. Yudias and co. use this unexpected break to go on a trip. As they tour all those places filled with memories, they visit the "Super Secret Theme Park" they saw in a local magazine. There, Yudias witnesses a very lackluster Duel Show, and he just can't take it...

100.SummaryEnglish: The robot Kuaidul left behind contains information on a card that can revive Velgearians. Asaka and co. work on their plan to complete that card and revive the Velgearians. However, there is someone obstructing their progress...

101.SummaryEnglish: Yuga and Yuhi's ideals clash against each other on the moon! Yuga has something he can't give up on, and Yuhi is shouldering a burden of his own. While their intense Duel is going on, the plan to revive the Velgearians is also progressing. The forbidden card is activated as a flash of light is unleashed from the Duel Control System!

102.SummaryEnglish: Yuamu decides to side with Yuga, who has been fighting by himself in space for the sake of the children in the future. He has been injured, so Yuamu takes up his Duel Disk and faces off against Yudias, who has inherited Yuhi's will. This battle with no winner is about to take a new turn!

103.SummaryEnglish: Yudias and co. venture into space once again using the Valvelgear! However, they are in a bind... because their only source of food on the ship is a huge pile of curry buns! Having gotten sick of curry buns, they try to create a new flavor. And so, they put curry buns and Space Dragon fabric into the Hyper Matter Blender...

104.SummaryEnglish: Due to the carelessness of their new traveling companion, Valvelgear CPT, Yuhi and co. are forced to make an emergency landing on the Mine Planet. The impact of the landing renders their bathroom unusable. A mysterious intruder known as Sabyuas then pops out of Yuhi's shadow. Yuhi has to try and hold it in as he Duels against Sabyuas, who's obstructing the bathroom's repairs!

105.SummaryEnglish: A relief package has arrived on the Valvelgear. However, what the crew finds isn't supplies, but rather, Manabu and Nyandestar. Everyone on the Valvelgear has been losing their minds from eating the same flavor of curry bread over and over again, and so, more chaos breaks out as they fight over a single sweet treat. Epoch and Manabu then Duel against each other to decide who should be captain and get the Valvelgear under control!

106.SummaryEnglish: Yudias and co. visit Planet Pawtner in search of a method to revive the Velgearians. When they investigate some ruins, they hear some voices saying "Mommy!". The sources of the voices turn out to be Darkman and Bleu Air, and they are specifically addressing Nyandestar. She refuses to accept that she's their mom, however, and begins a Duel!

108.SummaryEnglish: Yudias and co. are living on curry bread as per usual. But suddenly, Fukamura, a "big" shot from the Dark Matter Empire, appears before them! Intending to obtain some curry bread, Fukamura commences a Duel... Manabu, the Valvelgear's vice captain, takes it upon himself to defeat this new foe!

109.SummaryEnglish: Something has awakened within the dark matter vortex. A man suddenly descends on the Dark Matter Empire... Where he is brought to the castle and receives a Duel Disk with a Deck from the emperor, "Dark Meister". The two then converse through a Rush Duel.

110.SummaryEnglish: Yudias and co. discuss the mysteries surrounding Damamu, whose clones keep appearing and disappearing. However, Sabyuas then shows up on the Valvelgear again. Seeking the curry bread the Dark Meister desires, Sabyuas begins a Duel. The one who will face off against him is Epoch, the captain of the Valvelgear!

111.SummaryEnglish: Zuwijo, who once vanished, has appeared once again before Yudias and his friends. While Yudias is deeply moved by this unexpected reunion, Zuwijo demands a Duel with him, declaring himself as Darkman Zuwijo, the Dark Meister’s knight and the Black Blade of the Dark Matter Empire!

112.SummaryEnglish: Since Zuwijo is back,  it is possible that the 8.88 million comrades have also been revived, so the Valvelgear’s crew heads for the Velgear Cluster. However, Damamu has been acting even stranger than usual. In order to entertain Damamu and bring them back to normal, Yuhi challenges them to a Duel!

113.SummaryEnglish: Yudias and co. have ended up in the Dark Matter Zone due to CPT’s plan. They manage to find CPT within this zone, but upon talking to it, they find out it’s actually a different being called CPU. The group try to come up with a plan to escape from CPU and the Dark Matter Zone, but…

114.SummaryEnglish: Yudias and co. try to escape from the Dark Matter Zone, but end up in the Dark Matter Empire’s castle instead. In order to find out the truth behind all the mysteries, Yudias challenges the Dark Meister to a Duel. As Yuhi watches over their fierce battle, he feels an indescribable sense of unease…

115.TitleEnglish: Those Who Walk in the Dark
115.SummaryEnglish: The Dark Meister has revealed her identity, as well as the truth behind all the mysteries. Upon learning the sad truth behind the Dark Matter Zone’s existence and how it was created, Yudias is plagued with doubts. This is when someone unexpected extends a helping hand to him. The Dark Meister then speaks about her true motive. Just what is she after?

116.SummaryEnglish: The Dark Meister and the Darkmen head to Earth on the stolen Valvelgear. Yuhi learns the Dark Meister's true intentions and joins them, but when he bumps into Zuwjio on the ship, they get into an argument and decide to duel. Yuhi refuses to listen to whatever he has to say if he loses, but...

117.SummaryEnglish: Fukamura appears before Yudias and co., who are trying to find a way to pursue the Dark Meister. He then commences a Duel against Yudias, promising that he'll tell them how to catch up with the Dark Meister if Yudias wins. However, Yudias is hesitant about Dueling him?!

118.SummaryEnglish: The Dark Meister has arrived on Earth, sending Asaka and others into a panic! As the Darkmen begin their search for "Monster Reborn", Asaka and co. head to where it is hidden in order to protect it. This doesn't escape the notice of Sabyuas, however. Just what's going to happen as Sabyuas closes in on Asaka...?!

119.SummaryEnglish: Under the order of the Dark Meister, the Darkmen chase after Damamu, who has taken "Monster Reborn" and escaped. The Dark Meister uses the DM Particles to immobilize Damamu. Yuhi just can't bear to watch this, however, so he challenges the Dark Meister to a Duel.

120.SummaryEnglish: Thinking that the Rovian Currific Workers might be sheltering Damamu, Yudias and co. head to Badloon Castle. However, they run into Zeyet, who is also looking for Damamu. The two leaders, Rovian and Zeyet, clash against each other in a Duel, with Damamu on the line!

121.SummaryEnglish: Mutsuba Town is filled with the Goha Mark as the Goha Company's power rapidly grows. This is when Phaser declares that MIK will be absorbed into the Goha Company as part of a merger. Manabu just can't agree with Phaser's decision, however. In order to protect MIK, Manabu challenges Phaser to a Duel, with the position of MIK commander on the line!

122.SummaryEnglish: Desiring excellent gears that can be used to build drones, Yuna sends Zeyet to Kallister Gears. In order to use The☆Lugh to persuade Epoch, Zeyet puts some of her Dark Power into manga ink. However, she ends up unleashing Lugh's negative energy.

123.SummaryEnglish: Soy Sauce: A mystical liquid that can make mochi yummy with a single drop. Fukamura finds the Dark Meister's strict "one drop a day" policy very fishy, so he incites Sabyuas and the other Darkmen to take action. Angered that the Dark Meister is being insulted, Sabyuas challenges Fukamura to a Duel!

124.SummaryEnglish: The Darkmen have been desperately searching for "Monster Reborn". However, Yuna has a premonition and decides to pay Asaka a visit by herself. She gets to the Mutsuba Card Plant, and finds Asaka at a workbench with blueprints on it. She then challenges Asaka to a Duel, with everything they have on the line.

125.SummaryEnglish: Yuamu has finally obtained "Monster Reborn". Yuhi wants to stop her from erasing her own memories and becoming Otes, but Zeyet's brutally honest opinion destroys his soul. She says that his current outfit is too stupid, so he must buy some new clothes before Dueling Yuamu!

126.TitleEnglish: Let the Living be Sealed into the Light
126.SummaryEnglish: Yuamu begins a Duel in order to become Otes. Yuamu picks Yuhi as her opponent, but he just can't find the resolve to Duel her. This is when Yudias volunteers to Duel Yuamu in his place. What is Yudias going to do to stop Yuamu's plan?

127.TitleEnglish: The Dead Rise from the Darkness
127.SummaryEnglish: Yudias is desperately fighting to prevent Yuamu from becoming Otes. He manages to outwit Yuamu and land a direct attack. He thinks that he has won, but when the smoke clears, he sees Yuhi there, with his Duel Disk out. Yuhi has moved Yuamu out of the way, and is now facing Yudias. His eyes are filled with strong resolve.

128.TitleEnglish: Carve a Road Through It All and Press Onward
128.SummaryEnglish: Manabu and co. start a rebellion in order to stop Yuamu and Yuna's plan, but it ends in failure. They are then sent to an underground labor facility. Supervised by the Dark Drones, Manabu and co. are forced to toil in front of a giant device. As Manabu and Epoch try to find a way to escape, they discover an entrance to the giant device...

129.SummaryEnglish: With the new Otes at the helm, the Goha Company has transformed into a global corporation. Among those who have sided with the new Goha is a group that seeks to cause chaos and mayhem in the world. Intending to offer the rebels to Goha as a present, Tenten Nanahoshi comes along with the branch Nanahoshi family to challenge Yudias to a Duel!

130.SummaryEnglish: Asaka and co. sneak into the detention facility for rebels. There, they find Zaion waiting for them. In contrast to Mutsuba Heavy Industries, which has declined, Setsuri Furniture has successfully opened 88.8 billion stores by teaming up with Goha. The presidents of the two companies, Asaka and Zaion, begin a clash of ideals through a Duel!

131.SummaryEnglish: Manabu and co. escape from the detention facility and meet up with Yudias. However, they are discovered by Otes. He tells them that he’ll let them get away if they can beat Zuwijo in a Duel. Carrying his friends’ fate on his shoulders, Manabu begins the Duel! Will they obtain freedom…or life imprisonment?

132.TitleEnglish: A Cheer for Her Fated One!
132.SummaryEnglish: Yuna is fantasizing about living a married life with Yuga as usual. When Yuamu sees that, she thinks about how her future spouse is somewhere out there, since she has descendants in the future. Zeyet tells her that Zuwijo is her fated one, which causes her heart to pound...

133.SummaryEnglish: Yuhi, who has transformed into Otes, attacks UTS! Intending to seize both Yudias and Kuaidul, he attempts to kidnap Yudias, who is frozen in place. However, Yudias’s number one disciple, Epoch, challenges Yuhi to a Duel!

134.SummaryEnglish: Yudias, who is still frozen, has been taken to Yuna. Two Damamus chase after him, but end up getting trapped inside his mind. They are now in a world resembling Mutsuba Town. There, they discover a tiny Yudias.

135.SummaryEnglish: Yudias has awakened in the world inside his mind. He is guided to a science lab by a mysterious light. He is then greeted by Kuaidul. Sensing malice from Kuaidul, Yudias challenges him to a Duel. During the Duel, Yudias witnesses several different worlds…

136.SummaryEnglish: Yuna is willing to sacrifice Kuaidul and Kuyamuya to realize her own wish. Yuamu tries to stop her through a Duel but fails to prevent the activation of "Time Machine". Yuna wants to have a door to That Guy, and she is going to throw everything away to achieve that goal.

137.SummaryEnglish: Otes-Yuhi intends to travel through time and enter Yuga's era. He acquires "Time Machine" and transforms into a more sinister form. Yudias challenges Yuhi to a Duel, but he himself is filled with an unusual rage.

138.SummaryEnglish: Yuhi and Yudias' Duel keeps getting more and more intense. Due to the time travel system going out of control, information of the past and future becomes Time Power and overwhelms Yudias, causing him immense pain! And then, Yuhi undergoes another transformation...

139.SummaryEnglish: Otes is putting pressure on Yudias with his immense power. As Yudias bets everything on his draw, he manages to draw a card that he shouldn't be able to. Kuaidul then announces that "an alien warrior has obtained power equal to that of a devil through great growth!". Yudias no longer has any doubt or hesitation.

140.SummaryEnglish: After the fierce battle against Otes, Yudias and co. are engulfed by a bright light emitted by the time machine. Before they know it, they are now in the dark mountains. As they wander through the woods at night, Rinkage, a man who dresses like a ninja, appears and challenges them to a Duel!

141.SummaryEnglish: Rinkage's master, Gakugen Sogetsu, is the creator of the Sogetsu Style, as well as the ancestor of Maddox! In order to correct Gakugen's frivolous behavior, Maddox challenges him to a Duel. And so, a Rush Duel with the Sogetsu name on the line begins! Whoever loses will have to call himself "So Dead".

142.SummaryEnglish: Yudias and co. head to the castle of Gakugen's lord, Usu Otei, in order to talk to him. They run into a destroyed castle in the forest, and encounter a group that has been wreaking havoc in Usu Otei's domain. Their leader, the Princess of Beasts, then appears...

143.SummaryEnglish: Usu Otei told Yudias and co. that he has been using the power of Rush Duels to create peace. The conversation is interrupted by two brothers, Korasu Ryugu and Fazu Ryugu. The two begin a Duel in order to get revenge for being chased out of their domain. Usu Otei's retainers, the Four Dark Generals, then take on the brothers!

144.SummaryEnglish: Oteiusu plans to send the people that were defeated in Duels to the moon with a wooden rocket. After witnessing samurai getting stuffed into a rocket, Yudias challenges Oteiusu to a Duel. He is driven into a corner by Oteiusu's overwhelming ability, but manages to draw a fateful card!

145.TitleEnglish: The Letter That Leapt Through Time
145.SummaryEnglish: There is a letter hidden in the wooden Duel Disk discovered in the Mutsuba Mountains. It's written by Yuamu in the Sengoku era, and addressed to Asaka in the modern age. It's a challenge letter, with the sequence for the Duel recorded on it. In order to reactivate the time machine, Asaka and Yuamu will clash across space and time!

146.TitleEnglish: The Monk Who Can't Wait Until Tomorrow
146.SummaryEnglish: Rumor has it that a giant eight-foot-tall yokai is terrorizing children in the nearby village. Yudias and co. head to the beach in order to search for the yokai. There, they encounter the eight-foot-tall lady, Ferko Sur Oka. Ferko, who detests samurai, mistakes Yuhi for a samurai, so she challenges him to a Duel!

147.SummaryEnglish: Yudias and co. chase after Oteiusu, who has escaped from his prison. They find him talking to Tenten on the beach. Ranran suspects they are colluding with each other, while Tenten doesn't like being suspected. As the two of them argue, Oteiusu commences a Duel. The two Nanahoshis will now Tag Duel against him!

148.SummaryEnglish: The space-time gate goes haywire and ascends to the moon. As Usu Otei chases after the gate, Zuwijo challenges him to a Duel above the moon. Zuwijo was perplexed as he had to confront his hidden emotions, but now, he's regained his pride as a warrior after talking to Maddox. The proud alien warrior now heads off to his final battle!

149.SummaryEnglish: In order to stop Usu Otei's ambition, Yudias heads to the moon. However, the Varivelgear that he relies on for transport has stopped working. Learning about Yudias' tremendous growth, Yuhi and Yuamu vow to each other to help him out. A miracle then occurs as a bright light envelops the two of them...

150.SummaryEnglish: It’s time for the final battle! Yudias, Yuhi, and Yuamu land on the moon and challenge Otei Usu to a Duel. Otei Usu absorbs his other selves from parallel universes and takes on the three! As their fierce battle unfolds, a monster that Yudias doesn’t recall summoning appears behind him…

151.SummaryEnglish: The Dueling Space-Time is in flux. Even as they’re being toyed with by an inevitable end, Yudias and his friends still stand against Otei Usu! Will they be able to draw the card that will change the future?! Yuhi’s wings and Yuamu’s courage will help Yudias usher in a new era. The fun still isn’t over, for there are Duelists right here!
